ing mass scale of $\\sim\n10^{12}M_\\odot$. A quantitative measure of conformity in various properties,\nalong with its evolution, thus represents a new and stringent test of the\nimpact of quenching on environment within current galaxy formation models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Jul 2017 20:00:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 20 Dec 2017 07:34:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-31"}
