.g., DFT combined with dynamical mean-field theory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Jul 2017 13:22:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 16 Oct 2017 15:41:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-17"}
